Subject: Teamviewer File Transfer not blocked.
Description:
I have selected Teamviewer within the Exitpoint of content policy but it does not inspect or block the traffic which means sensitive content can be transferred out via teamviewer application.

Not sure if related but Teamviewer is listed as "Team viewer" within the admin policy GUI.  

- version of teamviewer is Teamviewer Host 15.60.3.0

Thanks
James
Solution_Comment__c:
Application was blocked by adding: 

teamviewer.exe 
Teamviewer
*teamviewer*
teamviewer*

and even the path toward the teamviewer.exe file (C:Program Files...)
